                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>Columbia</placeName>\n                <date>May 9<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> 1854</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Mr. Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dear Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">I have made the following<lb/> collections for you.</p>\n            <table cols=\"2\" rows=\"13\">\n                <row>\n                    <cell><persName>A Alexander</persName>\n                        <sic>sett</sic> P Books</cell>\n                    <cell>$18.00</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell><persName>S Wolf</persName> Bible</cell>\n                    <cell>9.00</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell><persName>L Elias</persName> Bible &amp; Occident</cell>\n                    <cell>15.00</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell><persName role=\"author\">I C Lyons</persName> “ “</cell>\n                    <cell>15.00</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell><persName>H Lyons</persName> “ “</cell>\n                    <cell>15.00</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell><persName>J Levin</persName>\n                        <persName>Dias</persName> &amp;. “</cell>\n                    <cell>3.75</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell><persName>B E Levy</persName> “</cell>\n                    <cell>3.00</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell><persName>J D Mordecai</persName> “</cell>\n                    <cell>3.00</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>Sunday School <persName>Peixotto</persName></cell>\n                    <cell>7.20</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell><persName>L J Levin</persName> Occident</cell>\n                    <cell>\n                        <hi rend=\"underline\">6.00</hi>\n                    </cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell>$94 95</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>to C<add>?</add> Ship &amp; R Road freight &amp;c 206 Prem on CK 44</cell>\n                    <cell>\n                        <hi rend=\"underline\">2 52</hi>\n                    </cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>Bal</cell>\n                    <cell>$92.43</cell>\n                </row>\n            </table>\n            <p>for which I enclose you a check.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\"><persName>Mr. L Carr</persName> is residing in <placeName>Augusta\n                    Geo.</placeName>\n                <persName>Mr.<lb/> Jno Barnett</persName> in <placeName>Charleston</placeName> that\n                latter I wrote<lb/> concerning his subscription to the books which he<lb/> declines\n                taking giving as a reason the length<lb/> of time they were getting out also that he\n                had<lb/> purchased a <sic>sett</sic> of books for his wife &amp;c &amp;c &amp;c<lb/>\n                all of which I believe as much as suits me</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">There appears to be considerable blundering<lb/> either with you or\n                the subscribers as to what they</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3cf9js9k/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
