                    "value": "<p>him by not including him in the list <persName>Mr &amp; Mr H L</persName><lb/>\n                <persName>Mr Levy</persName> &amp;c send remembrance</p>\n            <p>As soon as any more money comes in I will forward<lb/> it</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">Yrs truly</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(11)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">I C Lyons</persName>\n            </p>"
